An action is a text that provides context for a collection of images. It can be used to tell a story, showcase a portfolio, or share a memory. 
What is an image gallery? 
An image gallery is a collection of images displayed on a website
Image galleries can be used to showcase portfolios, sell products, or share memories
Image galleries can be added to the main content area or below the main section of a website
How to write an image gallery description? 
Consider answering questions your audience might have
Use the 5 W's: who, what, when, where, and why
Be creative to connect with your audience and enrich their experience
